description: Available at: https://openstudionetwork.com/keezer - Want to add a stronger rhythmic element to your solo lines and get more drum-like precision in your playing? Using only basic scales and a metronome, Geoffrey shows you how to practice alternating between triplets and 16th notes, as well as developing rhythmic independence between the hands. This lesson is fun and challenging! (Level: Intermediate/Adv.)
